%N A395827 a(n) is the number of possible outcomes having a run of 2 or more sixes when a die is rolled n times.
%H A395827 <a href="/index/Rec#order_03">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (11,-25,-30).
%F A395827 a(n) = A340156(6,n).
